</li>
<li id="cite_note-22"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-22">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><i>Histories</i>, Book VI, Chapter 1.</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-23"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-23">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Book IV, Chapters 140-141. The bridge had been partly broken down. Arriving at the bank, the king had a caller call for Histiaeus, who arrived in a fleet of boats to ferry him across and rebuild the bridge.</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-24"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-24">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFLang1968">Lang 1968</a>, p.&#160;25</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-25"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-25">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFLang1968">Lang 1968</a>, p.&#160;24</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-26"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-26">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFBoardmanHammondLewisOstwald1988">Boardman et al. 1988</a>, p.&#160;463, Part II, Chapter 8, <a href="/wiki/Oswyn_Murray" title="Oswyn Murray">Oswyn Murray</a>, The Ionian Revolt</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-27"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-27">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">The CAH article summarizes several historians whose fragments are similar to passages in Herodotus, to be found at <a href="#CITEREFBoardmanHammondLewisOstwald1988">Boardman et al. 1988</a>, pp.&#160;467–468</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-28"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-28">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFBoardmanHammondLewisOstwald1988">Boardman et al. 1988</a>, pp.&#160;461–462</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-29"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-29">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFBoardmanHammondLewisOstwald1988">Boardman et al. 1988</a>, p.&#160;464</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-30"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-30">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFBoardmanHammondLewisOstwald1988">Boardman et al. 1988</a>, p.&#160;486</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-31"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-31">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFGeorges2000">Georges 2000</a>, p.&#160;1</span>
</li>
</ol></div>
